data.description:
Introducing a modern gem in the sought-after Fox Creek neighborhood in Oakleaf Plantation! This pristine home, built just three years ago, boasts four bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. Step into the inviting open-concept design that seamlessly blends the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the spacious kitchen, featuring a large layout that is perfect for entertaining. Equipped with modern appliances and a convenient pantry, this kitchen is a chef's delight. Imagine hosting gatherings while effortlessly preparing meals in this stylish and functional space. With four bedrooms, there's room for everyone to have their own private retreat. The master suite offers a relaxing haven with its ensuite bathroom, dual sinks, and walk-in closet creating a perfect sanctuary. Additionally, the home includes another full bathroom to accommodate the needs of the remaining bedrooms and guests.Convenience is key, and this home complete with a two-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space. The property's young age ensures that you'll enjoy the benefits of contemporary construction and design.

Located in the Fox Creek @ Oakleaf Plantation Neighborhood, residents can take advantage of community amenities and the vibrant surroundings. This is not just a home; it's an opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort, style, and community. Don't miss the chance to make this modern residence your own!
